          <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Water Infrastructure Resiliency and Sustainability Act of 2018</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Environmental Protection Agency to establish a grant program&nbsp;for increasing the resiliency or adaptability of water systems (e.g., groundwater storage systems or wastewater treatment systems) to changes to the quality, quantity, or reliability of water resources.</p>]]></text>
